          "Switching to PureVida was one of the best decisions we made. Our team loves the water quality, and we're saving over $400 a month compared to our old bottled water service."
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="text-sm text-gray-500 not-italic">— Office Manager, Dallas-Area Business</cite>
